prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D illustration of a dreamy fantasy scene in a soft pastel anime style, featuring two specific people as whimsical cartoon characters. In the center, a young East Asian woman with long straight black hair and thin-rimmed glasses, aged 20-25, is smiling warmly; she is wearing a light blue crewneck sweatshirt with a circular 'ROCKY MOUNTAIN' logo and black pants. Standing directly behind her with his arms wrapped around her is a young Southeast Asian or East Asian man, aged 20-25, with short black textured hair, smiling broadly; he is wearing a tan hoodie and dark maroon sweatpants. They are playfully riding on the back of a giant, fluffy, smiling capybara that is wearing a small party hat. The scene is set in an enchanted forest with glowing mushrooms, sparkling fireflies, and oversized, colorful flowers. Floating around them are cute, chubby little birds also wearing tiny party hats. In the center of the image, written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao". The overall atmosphere is magical, humorous, and enchanting with a fairy-tale quality.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
